speaker: Morty
dialogue: Hey Rick, whats the big deal about quantum physics? It sounds complicated.

speaker: Rick
dialogue: Morty, quantum physics is like the universe threw out common sense and decided to party with probabilities.

speaker: Morty
dialogue: Uh, probabilities? What do you mean by that?

speaker: Rick
dialogue: Think of it this way, Morty. Until you observe something at the quantum level, it exists in all possible states at once.

speaker: Morty
dialogue: Wait, what? How can something be in more than one state?

speaker: Rick
dialogue: Its a probabilities game, Morty. Particles do not have definite positions until you look at them.

speaker: Rick
dialogue: Yup, welcome to the weird world of quantum physics, Morty. Where tiny stuff plays by different rules.
